      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's no way back. like everything i built is just zero. and the shame is so heavy... it's like it's part of who i am now. i look at the numbers and i look at the people i let down and i just see a dead end. there's no coming back from this kind of failure. everything is just... done.",
